{
    "initializationAction": [
        "q.player.data.dialogue.shelby || q.player.data.dialogue.bernard_confront == false ? q.dialogue.set_page('farewell');"
    ],
    "speakers": {
        "npc": {
            "name": {
                "type": "expression",
                "expression": "q.npc.name"
            },
            "face": "q.npc.face();",
            "gibber": {
                "interval": 0.1
            }
        },
        "player": {
            "face": "q.player.face();",
            "gibber": {
                "interval": 0.1
            },
            "name": {
                "type": "expression",
                "expression": "q.player.username"
            }
        }
    },
    "pages": [
        {
            "id": "greeting",
            "escapeAction": "0",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Hi, can I help you?"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": true,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Where are family records kept?",
                        "value": "1",
                        "action": [
                            "q.dialogue.set_page('1');"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "1",
            "escapeAction": "0",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Are you looking for anything in particular?"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": true,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Well, I need...",
                        "value": "2",
                        "action": [
                            "q.dialogue.set_page('2');"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "2",
            "escapeAction": "0",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Oh? Well our archives here only go back 200 years. So you're not in luck."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": true,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Do you know where I could?",
                        "value": "3",
                        "action": [
                            "q.dialogue.set_page('3');"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "3",
            "escapeAction": "0",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Well the only town that's been around for more than 400 years is Caligo."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": true,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Oh?",
                        "value": "4",
                        "action": [
                            "q.dialogue.set_page('4');"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "4",
            "escapeAction": "0",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "It's known as the \"town that survived\" and has been pretty much untouched since. I'd try talking to the historian, Petra, regarding that."
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": true,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Ok, thank you!",
                        "value": "4",
                        "action": [
                            "q.run_command('ftbquests change_progress ' + q.player.username + ' complete 27117840E01DAC02');",
                            "q.player.data.dialogue.shelby = true; q.player.save_data();",
                            "q.dialogue.close();"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        },
        {
            "id": "farewell",
            "speaker": "npc",
            "lines": [
                "Family trees are such a fascinating thing, don't you think?"
            ],
            "input": {
                "type": "option",
                "vertical": true,
                "options": [
                    {
                        "text": "Goodbye",
                        "value": "goodbye",
                        "action": [
                            "q.dialogue.close();"
                        ]
                    }
                ]
            }
        }
    ]
}